name: WINNING! (Scheduling My Interview)
description: The WINNING collection includes several astronauts, each with an alternate ending. This astronaut has cancelled countless interviews over the years. After a major move up, the astronaut is now dancing over to the phone. Music: ["Warrior"](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LvHHBRL5I1M) by Prod. Riddiman Artwork created by Luke Dillon.
collection_description: Artworks by professional artists inspired by Into The Cryptoverse.
